@OhhHeyItsLisa I was about to leave for work and decided to do a test thinking that it would for sure be negative 🙃 anyway now I don't know what do do with myself. Do my taxes? Clean out my closet? Scroll TikTok for 6 hours?

But hey, You get a few days off work? 🥴
@catietmckinlay hopefully that's the worst of it!! 💗
@AlyssaIsBright Thanks! I actually feel okay, just congested with a terrible headache.
